:Notes%20On%20Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Sketches a owl:NamedIndividual,
        rico:RecordSet,
        rico:Title ;
    rdfs:label "Notes on Elizabeth Simcoe sketches" ;
    rico:accruals "No further accruals are expected." ;
    rico:conditionsOfAccess "No restrictions on access." ;
    rico:conditionsOfUse "Records are in the public domain. There are no restrictions on reproduction for research and private study.  If you wish to use any of this material for a purpose other than research and private study, submit a Request for Permission to Publish, Exhibit or Broadcast Form." ;
    rico:creationDate "[ca. 1790-184--]" ;
    rico:generalDescription "Finding Aid Note: An online list is available for this sub-series." ;
    rico:hasContentOfType :Cartographic%20Materials,
        :Textual%20Records ;
    rico:hasOrHadIdentifier :F%2047-11-4 ;
    rico:hasOrHadInstantiation :Notes%20On%20Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Sketches-i1 ;
    rico:hasOrHadTitle :Notes%20On%20Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Sketches ;
    rico:hasRecordSetType :Sub-Series ;
    rico:history "Custodial History: The material in this sub-series was acquired in 1952 under the terms of a long-term loan agreement with the University of Toronto Library, which owns the records." ;
    rico:isDirectlyIncludedIn :Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Sketches ;
    rico:isOrWasDescribedBy :Notes%20On%20Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20Sketches%20Archival%20Description ;
    rico:scopeAndContent "Sub-series consists of records providing information about the artworks contained within sub-series F 47-11-1 to F 47-11-3. It is not clear whether Elizabeth Simcoe was the author of these documents. Two are caption lists of some of her sketches; the remaining two documents are scraps, containing a few names and notes. There is also a map indicating places where Elizabeth Simcoe made sketches." .

